<heading>move - Move a portable box.</heading>
<rule/>
<heading level="2">Usage</heading>
<pre>move NAME --box BOX</pre>
<heading level="2">Description</heading>
<paragraph>Moves a portable box from the current location into another box at the same location.</paragraph>
<heading level="2">Examples</heading>
<pre>move Key --box Drawer
  Move the Key into the Drawer box.</pre>
<heading level="2">See also</heading>
<paragraph>drop, inv, look, place, take</paragraph>
